articles.title: Biden commemorates Veterans Day as conflicts escalate abroad - POLITICO
articles.description: Although Biden did not explicitly mention the ongoing conflicts in Ukraine and Gaza, his speech focused on American forces rising to the occasion to defeat darkness and evil.
articles.content:
Biden was joined by Vice President Kamala Harris, Secretary of Veterans Affairs Denis McDonough and top military officials.
